Swappy: Face Swap & Deepfake Privacy Policy
Welcome to Swappy!
Swappy is a creative app designed to help you swap faces, experiment with deepfake technologies, and transform your photos and videos effortlessly. Your privacy is our priority, and we are committed to safeguarding your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your data. By downloading or using Swappy, you agree to this Privacy Policy, which is part of our Terms of Use.
Key Highlights
Purpose of the App
Swappy allows users to create unique face-swapped media and experiment with deepfake features. All processing is designed solely for user-requested editing and visualization, ensuring your control over the content.
Face Data Storage Policy
The length of time face data is stored and why it is stored for this specific length of time:
Face data is stored
temporarily for the duration of the editing session only.
Once the user completes the editing session and the media is processed,
all face data is permanently deleted.
This ensures your data is only retained as long as necessary to fulfill your request and is not stored beyond the required timeframe.
1. INFORMATION WE COLLECT
1.1. Content Selection and Processing
Photos and Videos:
Swappy processes only the specific photos or videos you choose for editing. We do not access your entire media library.
Encryption:
All selected content is encrypted and temporarily cached on secure servers during the editing session. After processing, the data is immediately deleted.
Metadata Removal:
Any metadata, such as geotags, is automatically stripped from uploaded content.
1.2. Additional Information
We collect data related to app usage, such as:
Language settings, installation times, and usage patterns.
Device information (e.g., operating system, model, IP address).
Subscription status and purchase history (excluding sensitive billing details).
This information is anonymized and used to improve app functionality and user experience.
1.3. Contacting Us
For any privacy-related questions or concerns, please contact us at
oodrills@oodrillsapp.com
.
2. HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION
Delivering app features and ensuring smooth functionality.
Enhancing security, troubleshooting issues, and analyzing trends.
Developing and testing new features.
Customizing your app experience and advertisements.
Uploaded content is only used to provide the requested services during the active session and is deleted immediately afterward. Swappy
does not use face data for biometric processing or user identification.
If we need to use your information for any other purpose, we will notify you in advance and obtain your explicit consent if required.
3. HOW WE SHARE YOUR INFORMATION
3.1. Protecting Your Content
Your photos, videos, and face data are
never shared with third parties.
3.2. Sharing Non-Visual Information
We may share anonymized or aggregated data under the following conditions:
Service Providers:
For hosting, analytics, or support services.
Advertising Partners:
To display relevant app-related ads.
Professional Advisors:
In compliance with legal or auditing requirements.
Business Transfers:
In the event of mergers or acquisitions.
4. DATA STORAGE AND SECURITY
Data Retention
Face Data:
Temporarily stored for the editing session only and permanently deleted afterward.
Other Data:
Retained only as long as necessary to fulfill app-related purposes.
Data Security
We use industry-standard encryption and secure servers to protect your data. However, no system can guarantee absolute security.
5. LINKS TO THIRD-PARTY SERVICES
Swappy may contain links to third-party platforms. We do not control these services, and their privacy practices are governed by their own policies.
6. UPDATING THE PRIVACY POLICY
We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in practices or legal requirements. Updates will be posted in the app and on our website. Continued use of Swappy indicates acceptance of the revised terms.
